pen%20the%20channel%20to%20one%20of%20the%20busiest%20ports%20in%20the%20US.%20On%20Saturday%2C%20the%20Governor%20of%20Maryland%20said%20officials%20planned%20to%20remove%20the%20first%20piece%20of%20the%20debris.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChris%20James%2C%20the%20employee%20of%20a%20consulting%20firm%20that's%20helping%20the%20ship's%20management%20company%2C%20Synergy%20Marine%2C%20told%20NYT%20the%20crew%20members%20have%20ample%20supplies%20of%20food%20and%20water%2C%20enough%20fuel%20to%20keep%20the%20generators%20working.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20there%20is%20still%20no%20exact%20timeline%20for%20when%20the%20ship%20might%20be%20extracted%20from%20the%20wreckage%2C%20Mr%20James%20told%20NYT.%20Once%20the%20National%20Transportation%20Safety%20Board%20(NTSB)%20and%20the%20Coast%20Guard%20finish%20their%20investigations%2C%20the%20crew%20may%20be%20swapped%20to%20be%20sent%20home%2C%20Mr%20James%20said%20in%20the%20NYT%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20crew%20has%20received%20praise%20for%20sending%20SOS%20messages%20to%20the%20local%20authorities%20which%20allowed%20them%20to%20stop%20much%20of%20the%20traffic%20before%20the%20accident.%20Six%20people%20who%20were%20part%20of%20a%20construction%20crew%20repairing%20potholes%20on%20the%20bridge%20were%20killed%20when%20the%20structure%20collapsed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20information%20is%20that%20there%20are%2021%20crew%20members%2C%20of%20which%2020%20are%20Indians.%20All%20of%20them%20are%20in%20good%20shape%2C%20good%20health.%20One%20of%20them%20got%20injured%20slightly%2C%20needed%20to%20have%20some%20stitches%2C%20and%20stitches%20have%20been%20given.%20And%2C%20he%20has%20gone%20back%20to%20the%20ship%2C%26quot%3B%20MEA%20spokesperson%20Randhir%20Jaiswal%20had%20said%20in%20response%20to%20a%20query%20during%20his%20weekly%20media%20briefing%20in%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711862820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2F5kq628r8_baltimore_625x300_31_March