ldn't%20succeed%20in%20small%20towns%20because%20nobody%20would%20buy%20a%20%E2%82%B9300%20coffee.%20Meanwhile%20Varanasi%2C''%20the%20video%20was%20captioned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWatch%20the%20video%20here%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EPeople%20earlier%20%3A%20Starbucks%20wouldn't%20succeed%20in%20small%20towns%20because%20nobody%20would%20buy%20a%20%E2%82%B9300%20coffee.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnMeanwhile%20Varanasi%20%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FKYfSJt1WQ3%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FKYfSJt1WQ3%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Aaraynsh%20(%40aaraynsh)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Faaraynsh%2Fstatus%2F1773594774219448826%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMarch%2029%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EReacting%20to%20the%20video%2C%20one%20user%20wrote%2C%20It's%20just%20an%20opening%20ceremony%20maybe%20that's%20why%20people%20just%20wanna%20try%20it%20but%20yeah%20it%20will%20be%20successful%20all%20thanks%20to%20social%20media%20status.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20commented%2C%20''I%20didn't%20see%20this%20coming%20in%20a%20million%20years!%20Rameshwaram%20cafe%20feels.''%20A%20third%20said%2C%20''In%20initial%20days%20you%20will%20find%20the%20same%20queue%2C%20just%20to%20get%20clicked%20with%20Starbucks%20cup%20and%20to%20post%20it%20on%20insta%2C%20after%20few%20days%20only%20real%20coffee%20lovers%20will%20come%20When%20it%20was%20started%20in%20Indore%2C%20there%20were%20queue%20for%202-3%20hrs%20to%20get%20into%20the%20cafe.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20fourth%20added%2C%20''Benares%20is%20by%20no%20means%20a%20small%20town.%20The%20city%20also%20happens%20to%20be%20a%20magnet%20for%20national%20and%20international%20tourists%2C%20home%20to%20two%20universities%2C%20one%20affiliated%20with%20IIT%2C%20and%20represented%20by%20Modi%20in%20the%20parliament.''%20A