0Wife%20To%20Address%20Mega%20Rally%20At%20Ramlila%20Maidan%20Today%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20'Loktantra%20Bachao'%20(Save%20Democracy)%20rally%2C%20which%20will%20be%20held%20at%20Ramlila%20Maidan%20in%20the%20national%20capital%2C%20has%20been%20organised%20after%20the%20arrest%20of%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20in%20the%20Delhi%20liquor%20policy%20scam%20last%20week%20but%20is%20being%20seen%20as%20a%20show%20of%20strength%20and%20unity%20by%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20ahead%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20opposition%20is%20expected%20to%20speak%20out%20strongly%20against%20what%20it%20calls%20the%20BJP's%20misuse%20of%20central%20agencies%20like%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%2C%20CBI%2C%20and%20the%20Income%20Tax%20Department.%20The%20issue%20has%20taken%20centre%20stage%20after%20the%20arrests%20of%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20and%20former%20Jharkhand%20chief%20minister%20Hemant%20Soren%2C%20and%20the%20tax%20notices%20issued%20to%20the%20Congress%2C%20including%20one%20for%20Rs%201%2C800%20crore%20which%20was%20sent%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESome%20of%20the%20leaders%20in%20attendance%20will%20be%20Congress%20President%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%2C%20senior%20party%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20Samajwadi%20Party%20President%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%2C%20NCP%20(Sharadchandra%20Pawar)%20chief%20Sharad%20Pawar%2C%20Shiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%20chief%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%2C%20Senior%20RJD%20leader%20and%20former%20Bihar%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20Tejashwi%20Yadav.%20Jharkhand%20Chief%20Minister%20Champai%20Soren%2C%20National%20Conference%20President%20Farooq%20Abdullah%2C%20PDP%20chief%20Mehbooba%20Mufti%2C%20and%20the%20DMK's%20Tiruchi%20Siva.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20Trinamool%20Congress%2C%20which%20had%20jolted%20the%20alliance%20by%20deciding%20to%20go%20it%20alone%20in%20West%20Bengal%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20is%20also%20likely%20to%20send%20a%20representative.%20The%20party's%20leader%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%20Derek%20O'Brien%2C%20is%20expected%20to%20share%20the%20stage%20with%20representatives%20from%20the%20Left%20parties%2C%20including%20Sitaram%20Yechury%20of%20the%20CPM%2C%20which%20is%20his%20party's%20bitter%20rival%20in%20West%20Bengal.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EFrom%20the%20AAP%2C%20Punjab%20Chief%20Minister%20Bhagwant%20Mann%20will%20be%20at%20the%20rally%20with%20other%20senior%20leaders.%20Arvind%20Kejriwal's%20wife%2C%20Sunita%20Kejriwal%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20present%20and%20Hemant%20Soren's%20wife%2C%20Kalpana%20Soren%2C%20will%20also%20attend.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwill-fight-together-say-sunita-kejriwal-kalpana-soren-as-arvind-kejriwal-hemant-soren-in-jail-5340155%5C%22%3EMs%20Kejriwal%20and%20Ms%20Soren%20had%20met%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Friday%20and%20said%20they%20have%20decided%20to%20%26quot%3Btake%20the%20fight%20forward%20together%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIt%20is%20unclear%20whether%20Ms%20Kejriwal%2C%20who%20has%20taken%20a%20more%20public%20role%20after%20her%20husband's%20arrest%20and%20has%20been%20accused%20by%20BJP%20leaders%20of%20preparing%20to%20take%20over%20the%20chief%20minister's%20chair%2C%20will%20speak%20at%20the%20rally.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20said%20the%20rally%20will%20send%20a%20%26quot%3Bstrong%20message%26quot%3B%20to%20Lok%20Kalyan%20Marg%2C%20where%20the%20Prime%20Minister's%20residence%20is%20located%2C%20that%20the%20BJP-led%20government's%20%26quot%3Btime%20is%20up%26quot%3B.%20Senior%20Congress%20leader%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20not%20a%20person-specific%20rally.%20That%20is%20why%20it%20is%20called%20Loktantra%20Bachao%20rally.%20This%20is%20not%20one%20party's%20rally%2C%20about%2027-28%20parties%20are%20involved.%20All%20constituents%20of%20the%20INDIA%20%3Cem%3E'janbandhan'%3C%2Fem%3E%20will%20be%20taking%20part%20in%20the%20rally.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20AAP%20has%20received%20permission%20from%20the%20authorities%20to%20hold%20the%20rally%20with%20more%20than%2020%2C000%20people.%20AAP's%20Punjab%20working%20president%2C%20Budh%20Ram%2C%20said%20the%20party%20has%20set%20a%20target%20of%20over%201%20lakh%20people%20from%20the%20state%20participating%20in%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20Delhi%20Traffic%20Police%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Findia-blocs-rally-in-delhi-tomorrow-delhi-traffic-police-advisory-routes-to-avoid-diversions-5340186%5C%22%3Eissued%20an%20advisory%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20said%20restrictions%20and%20diversions%20will%20be%20in%20place%20on%20several%20roads%20from%209%20am%20to%203%20pm%20today.%20Commuters%20have%20been%20advised%20to%20avoid%20the%20routes%20and%20use%20public%20transport%2C%20especially%20the%20Metro%2C%20as%20far%20as%20possible.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20maintained%20that%20both%20Arvind%20Kejriwal's%20arrest%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20and%20the%20tax%20notices%20to%20the%20Congress%20were%20the%20result%20of%20the%20agencies%20acting%20independently%20and%20following%20legal%20procedures.%20It%20has%20also%20hit%20out%20at%20the%20AAP%20for%20insisting%20on%20the%20Delhi%20chief%20minister%20running%20the%20government%20from%20jail.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711860300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fptcjhppg_india-bloc-meeting_625x300_17_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-elections-2024-after-arvind-kejriwals-arrest-india-blocs-mega-show-of-strength-today-5341955%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22After%20the%20arrest%20of%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%2C%20the%20AAP%20has%20organised%20a%20mega%20rally%20in%20Delhi%20today%2C%20which%20will%20be%20attended%20by%20key%20leaders%20of%20the%20Opposition%20INDIA%20bloc%2C%20including%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%2C%20and%20Akhilesh%20Yadav.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-elections-2024-after-arvind-kejriwals-arrest-india-blocs-mega-show-of-strength-today-5341955%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Navy%20vs%20Pirates%20Of%20The%20Arabian%3A%20Inside%20India's%20Daring%20Red%20Sea%20Missions%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20Navy%20carried%20out%2018%20rescue%20ops%20in%20the%20Arabian%20Sea%20since%20mid-December%20under%20its%20Operation%20Sankalp%2C%20launched%20after%20attacks%20on%20merchant%20ships%20in%20the%20Gulf%20of%20Oman%20in%20June%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Navy%20has%20been%20responding%20to%20the%20manifestation%20of%20the%20Israel-Hamas%20conflict%20in%20the%20maritime%20domain%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20Red%20Sea%20corridor%20-%20one%20of%20the%20world's%20busiest%20cargo%20and%20oil%20transit%20points%20-%20since%20December%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Navy%20responded%20to%20at%20least%2018%20incidents%20between%20December%202023%20and%20March%202024%20and%20played%20a%20pivotal%20role%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Bfirst%20responder%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20%26quot%3Bpreferred%20security%20partner%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20Indian%20Ocean%20Region%2C%20it%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%20During%20this%20period%2C%20the%20Navy%20came%20to%20the%20aid%20of%20several%20nations%20as%20the%20menace%20of%20pirate%20attacks%20in%20this%20major%20trade%20route%20was%20compounded%20by%20drone%20and%20missile%20strikes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20Navy%20Secured%20A%20Pirate%20Mother%20Ship%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPirates%20hijacked%20a%20Malta-flagged%20cargo%20vessel%20with%20the%20call%20sign%20Ruen%20on%20December%2014%2C%202023.%20An%20SOS%20was%20sent%20out%20by%20the%20crew%20onboard%20and%20the%20Navy%20began%20tracking%20it%20as%20soon%20as%20it%20was%20indicated%20that%20six%20pirates%20had%20illegally%20boarded%20it%20in%20the%20Arabian%20Sea.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20deployed%20a%20warship%20on%20anti-piracy%20patrol%20in%20the%20Gulf%20of%20Aden%20to%20locate%20and%20assist%20the%20seized%20vehicle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-media-max-width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FIndianNavy%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23IndianNavy%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20responded%20to%20the%20manifestation%20of%20Israel%20%E2%80%93%20Hamas%20conflict%20in%20the%20maritime%20domain%20by%20re-orienting%20%26amp%3B%20significantly%20enhancing%20the%20scope%20of%20its%20ongoing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2Fmaritimesecurityoperations%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23maritimesecurityoperations%3C%2Fa%3E%20since%20mid-Dec%2023.%20The%20navy%20undertook%20proactive%20actions%20during%20the%20hijacking%20of%20Malta%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fr5dNiW6PN4%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2Fr5dNiW6PN4%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20SpokespersonNavy%20(%40indiannavy)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Findiannavy%2Fstatus%2F1771522408123646088%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMarch%2023%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%20it%20was%20indicated%20that%20a%20crew%20of%20the%20vessel%20had%20been%20injured.%20The%20Navy%20launched%20a%20rescue%20op%20and%20evacuated%20the%20injured%20sailor%20from%20the%20vessel%20within%20four%20days.%20He%20was%20then%20flown%20to%20Oman%20for%20treatment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20pirates%20overtook%20control%20of%20MV%20Ruen%20and%20steered%20it%20towards%20the%20Somalian%20coast.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20then%2C%20at%20least%20a%20dozen%20warships%20have%20been%20deployed%20in%20the%20Gulf%20of%20Aden%20and%20the%20northern%20Arabian%20Sea%20to%20assist%20vessels%20east%20of%20the%20Red%20Sea%2C%20where%20the%20navies%20of%20several%20countries%2C%20including%20the%20US%2C%20are%20trying%20to%20secure%20the%20route%20from%20Yemen's%20Houthi%20rebels.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20hijacking%2C%20the%20Navy%20kept%20the%20region%20under%20%26quot%3Bcontinuous%20surveillance%20activities%26quot%3B%2C%20using%20aerial%20platforms%20and%20other%20vessels%20to%20gather%20information%20and%20monitor%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20days%20and%20three%20months%20later%2C%20MV%20Ruen%20was%20spotted%20off%20the%20Somali%20coast%20on%20March%2014%2C%20information%20came%20in%20from%20the%20British%20maritime%20security%20firm%20Ambrey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20pirates%20converted%20the%20bulk%20carrier%20into%20a%20mothership%20to%20attack%20other%20ships.%20On%20March%2015%2C%20the%20Indian%20Navy%20re-routed%20its%20warship%20INS%20Kolkata%20to%20intercept%20it.%20INS%20Kolkata%20sailed%20over%202%2C600%20km%20and%20cornered%20the%20vessel%20the%20next%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EForty%20hours%20later%2C%20the%20Navy%20forced%2035%20Somali%20pirates%20to%20surrender%20and%20rescued%2017%20crew%20members%20held%20hostage%20on%20the%20hijacked%20ship.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20high-stakes%20op%20involved%20multiple%20Navy%20vessels%2C%20drones%2C%20aircraft%2C%20and%20marine%20commandos.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EINS%20Subhadra%20-%20a%20patrol%20vessel%2C%20High%20Altitude%20Long%20Endurance%20(HALE%20RPA)%20drones%2C%20and%20P8I%20maritime%20patrol%20aircraft%20joined%20forces%20to%20help%20INS%20Kolkata%20take%20control%20of%20the%20pirate%20mother-ship.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20squad%20of%20eight%20marine%20commandos%20(MARCOS%20PRAHARs)%20were%20airdropped%20by%20a%20C-17%20aircraft%20onto%20the%20vessel%20to%20detain%20the%20pirates%20and%20safely%20evacuate%20the%20crew.%20No%20injuries%20were%20reported%20during%20the%20audacious%20operation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENavy%20To%20The%20Rescue%20Of%20Pakistani%20Nationals%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%