20Notably%2C%20she%C2%A0had%20a%20breast%20enlargement%20performed%20several%20years%20ago%20but%20had%20returned%20to%20have%20an%20imbalance%20corrected.%20The%20surgery%20cost%20her%20%2411%2C650%20(Rs%C2%A09%2C71%2C416).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20aspiring%20model%2C%20who%20had%20a%20pre-existing%20heart%20condition%2C%20suffered%20a%20heart%20attack%2C%20as%20a%20reaction%20to%20the%20anaesthetic%20and%20went%20into%20cardiac%20arrest.%C2%A0She%20was%20admitted%20to%20the%20intensive%20care%20unit%20at%20Son%20Espases%20University%20Hospital%20in%20Palma%20but%20died%20on%20September%2014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20family%20said%20that%20all%20the%20preceding%20consultations%20had%20been%20conducted%20by%20email%2C%20and%20claimed%20that%20the%20clinic%20had%20taken%20very%20few%20precautions%20beforehand.%C2%A0A%20police%20investigation%20was%20launched%20after%20the%20woman's%20family%20accused%20the%20cosmetic%20surgeons%20of%20malpractice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Majorcan%20newspaper%20Ultima%20Hora%2C%20the%20clinic's%20manager%20and%20anaesthetist%20have%20been%20arrested.%C2%A0The%20manager%2C%2069%2C%20has%20been%20charged%20with%20gross%20negligence%20manslaughter%20as%20well%20as%20carrying%20out%20the%20surgery%20despite%20being%20disqualified.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20National%20Police%2C%20the%20procedure%20involved%20several%20irregularities.%20The%20first%20was%20that%20the%20health%20professionals%20agreed%20to%20practice%20a%20second%20cosmetic%20procedure%20without%20warning%20the%20patient%20of%20the%20risks.%20She%20suffered%20from%20a%20congenital%20heart%20defect%20which%20meant%2025%25%20of%20her%20heart%20did%20not%20function%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20the%20signed%20patient%20consent%20forms%20were%20written%20in%20Spanish%20and%20the%20patient%20didn't%20know%20how%20to%20read%20Spanish.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20spokesman%20for%20Spanish%20National%20Police%20said%2C%20''National%20Police%20officers%20have%20arrested%20a%2069-year-old%20man%20responsible%20for%20managing%20a%20clinic%20in%20Palma%20where%20he%20also%20worked%20as%20a%20practitioner%2C%20for%20crimes%20of%20gross%20negligence%20manslaughter%20and%20breaching%20a%20medical%20ban%20following%20the%20death%20of%20a%20patient.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOur%20homicide%20unit%20began%20an%20investigation%20and%20after%20gathering%20together%20all%20the%20documentation%20related%20to%20the%20medical%20intervention%20and%20taking%20statements%20from%20health%20professionals%2C%20arrested%20the%20director%20of%20the%20clinic%20who%20was%20also%20a%20medical%20practitioner.%20Investigators%20have%20accused%20one%20of%20the%20other%20two%20health%20professionals%20who%20participated%20in%20the%20surgery%20of%20the%20same%20type%20of%20manslaughter%20crime%20as%20the%20clinic%20director.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20Ms%20Butterfield%20was%20a%20successful%20beauty%20entrepreneur%20with%20her%20own%20hair%20extension%20business%20under%20the%20name%20'Donna%20Bee'%20and%20'BeeWeavible'.%20A%20close%20family%20member%20said%2C%20''We'll%20never%20get%20over%20it%2C%20we%20just%20have%20to%20learn%20to%20live%20with%20it.''%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711853580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fe1soavjo_donna-butterfield_625x300_31_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fbritish-model-30-dies-after-botched-breast-enlargement-surgery-in-spain-5343293%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ms%20Butterfield%2C%20who%20had%20a%20pre-existing%20heart%20condition%2C%20suffered%20a%20heart%20attack%2C%20as%20a%20reaction%20to%20the%20anaesthetic%20and%20went%20into%20cardiac%20arrest%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fbritish-model-30-dies-after-botched-breast-enlargement-surgery-in-spain-5343293%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A