e%2C%20daughter%20of%20the%20party's%20patriarch%20Sharad%20Pawar%2C%20going%20up%20against%20Sunetra%20Pawar%2C%20wife%20of%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Ajit%20Pawar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBaramati%2C%20in%20Pune%20district%2C%20has%20evolved%20over%20the%20years%20from%20facing%20devastating%20famines%20into%20a%20thriving%20hub%20of%20agriculture%2C%20industry%2C%20and%20commerce.%20Decades%20of%20Pawar%20family%20dominance%20have%20shaped%20the%20political%20narrative%20of%20this%20region.%20The%20Pawar%20family's%20influence%20has%20been%20integral%20to%20this%20transformation%2C%20with%20Sharad%20Pawar's%20political%20career%20tracing%20back%20to%20the%201960s%20when%20he%20first%20won%20in%20this%20constituency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ESchism%20In%20The%20Family%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20emergence%20of%20two%20factions%20within%20the%20NCP%2C%20led%20by%20Sharad%20Pawar%20and%20his%20nephew%20Ajit%20Pawar%2C%20has%20set%20the%20stage%20for%20a%20dramatic%20electoral%20showdown.%20The%20NCP's%20founding%20faction%20has%20nominated%20Supriya%20Sule%2C%2054%2C%20while%20Sunetra%20Pawar%2C%2060%20and%20Ms%20Sule's%20sister-in-law%2C%20has%20entered%20the%20fray%20as%20the%20candidate%20representing%20the%20rival%20faction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20July%202%20last%20year%2C%20Ajit%20Pawar%2C%20accompanied%20by%20eight%20NCP%20MLAs%2C%20aligned%20with%20the%20Eknath%20Shinde%20administration%2C%20prompting%20a%20fracture%20within%20the%20NCP%20party%20ranks.%20The%20division%20within%20the%20NCP%20has%20left%20voters%20and%20party%20workers%20with%20a%20choice%20between%20two%20Pawars.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20will%20be%20a%20very%20tough%20choice%20for%20voters%20and%20party%20workers%20to%20choose%20between%20two%20Pawars.%20It%20is%20a%20contest%20they%20would%20never%20have%20imagined%20before%20July%202%20last%20year%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Madan%20Devkate%2C%20a%20local%20leader%2C%20as%20quoted%20by%20news%20agency%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%201960s%2C%20the%20Baramati%20Lok%20Sabha%20constituency%2C%20encompassing%20Baramati%2C%20Indapur%2C%20Daund%2C%20Purandar%2C%20Bhor%2C%20and%20Khadakwasla%20assembly%20seats%2C%20has%20served%20as%20Sharad%20Pawar's%20stronghold.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAjit%20Pawar%20has%20represented%20Baramati%20as%20an%20MLA%20since%201991%2C%20and%20had%20registered%20a%20resounding%20victory%20in%202019%20by%20securing%20an%20astonishing%2083%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20vote%20share.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ESupriya%20vs%20Sunetra%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Baramati%20Lok%20Sabha%20constituency%20consists%20of%20six%20assembly%20segments%3A%20Baramati%20town%2C%20Indapur%2C%20Daund%2C%20Purandar%2C%20Bhor%2C%20and%20Khadakwasla.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWithin%20these%20segments%2C%20the%20Congress%20holds%20sway%20over%20Bhor%20and%20Purandar%2C%20while%20Baramati%20and%20Indapur%20have%20historically%20favoured%20the%20NCP%20(prior%20to%20its%20division).%20The%20BJP%20holds%20influence%20in%20Daund%20and%20Khadakwasala.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%202019%20elections%2C%20Supriya%20Sule%20clinched%20her%20third%20consecutive%20win%20in%20the%20Baramati%20constituency%20under%20the%20NCP%20banner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENCP%20(SP)%20-%20the%20Sharad%20Pawar%20faction%2C%20a%20member%20of%20the%20opposition%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi%20(MVA)%2C%20along%20with%20Shiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%20and%20Congress%2C%20will%20vie%20for%2010%20seats%20in%20Maharashtra%2C%20a%20state%20with%2048%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats.%20Baramati's%20polls%20are%20scheduled%20for%20the%20third%20phase%20on%20May%207.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Sule%2C%20aged%2054%2C%20this%20marks%20her%20debut%20in%20a%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20where%20the%20NCP's%20support%20base%20will%20be%20divided%20between%20followers%20of%20her%20father%20and%20her%20cousin.%20While%20Sule%20relies%20on%20the%20allegiance%20of%20the%20Pawar%20Clan's%20supporters%20and%20her%20track%20record%20as%20a%20Lok%20Sabha%20representative%2C%20Ajit%20Pawar%20can%20garner%20additional%20backing%20from%20Shiv%20Sena%20cadres%20under%20Chief%20Minister%20Eknath%20Shinde's%20leadership%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20BJP%20candidate%20Kanchan%20Kul%2C%20wife%20of%20Daund%20MLA%20Rahul%20Kul%2C%20suffered%20defeat%20to%20Ms%20Sule%20by%20a%20margin%20of%20over%201.55%20lakh%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Sule's%20victory%20margin%20in%20Baramati%20during%20her%20debut%20Lok%20Sabha%20contest%20in%202009%20was%203%2C36%2C831%20against%20BJP%20nominee%20Kanta%20Nalawade.%20This%20margin%20decreased%20to%2069%2C719%20in%202014%20when%20Rashtriya%20Samaj%20Paksha%20leader%20Mahadev%20Jankar%20contested%20against%20her.%20In%202019%2C%20Ms%20Sule's%20vote%20tally%20surged%20to%206%2C86%2C714%20with%20a%20vote%20share%20of%2052.63%25%2C%20securing%20victory%20by%20over%201.55%20lakh%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESunetra%20Pawar%20is%20the%20second%20member%20of%20Ajit%20Pawar's%20family%20to%20contest%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%20In%202019%2C%20Ajit's%20son%20Parth%20contested%20from%20the%20Maval%20seat%20in%20Pune%20district%20but%20was%20defeated%20by%20Shiv%20Sena's%20Shrirang%20Barne.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESunetra%20Pawar%20hails%20from%20a%20politically%20active%20family%20in%20Marathwada.%20She%20is%20the%20sister%20of%20Padamsinh%20Patil%2C%20a%20former%20minister%20who%20initially%20belonged%20to%20the%20Congress%20but%20later%20joined%20Sharad%20Pawar's%20NCP%20in%201999.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711853160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fktomkdf8_supriya-sule-sunetra-pawar-_625x300_31_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F2024-lok-sbaha-elections-pawar-vs-pawar-in-maharashtra-as-supriya-sule-takes-on-sister-in-law-sunetra-pawar-5343351%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20Maharashtra's%20Baramati%2C%20a%20historic%20showdown%20awaits%20as%20the%20splintered%20National%20Congress%20Party%20(NCP)%20gears%20up%20for%20a%20unique%20'Pawar%20vs%20Pawar'%20contest%20in%20Supriya%20Sule%2C%20daughter%20of%20the%20party's%20patriarch%20Sharad%20Pawar%2C%20going%20up%20against%20Sunetra%20Pawar.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F2024-lok-sbaha-elections-pawar-vs-pawar-in-maharashtra-as-supriya-sule-takes-on-sister-in-law-sunetra-pawar-5343351%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22RR%20Star%20%26quot%3BNot%20Happy%26quot%3B%20To%20See%20Riyan%20Parag%20Rip%20Apart%20Anrich%20Nortje.%20Here's%20Why%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ERajasthan%20Royals%20stars%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Riyan%20Parag%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F108566-riyan-parag-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERiyan%20Parag%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Nandre%20Burger%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F113424-nandre-burger-playerprofile%5C%22%3ENandre%20Burger%3C%2Fa%3E%20shared%20a%20lighthearted%20banter%20after%20helping%20their%20team%20beat%20Delhi%20Capitals%20(IPL)%20in%20an%20IPL%202024%20match%20on%20Thursday.%20A%20rejuvenated%20Parag%20stole%20the%20show%20with%20the%20bat%2C%20clobbering%20an%20unbeaten%20knock%20of%2084%20runs%20off%2045%20balls%2C%20taking%20RR%20to%20185%2F5%20in%2020%20overs.%20Burger%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20returned%20figures%20of%202%2F29%2C%20including%20two%20wickets%20in%20the%20same%20over%20to%20dent%20DC's%20chase.%20RR%20held%20on%20for%20a%20narrow%2012-run%20win%20as%20DC%20could%20only%20manage%20173%2F5%20in%2020%20overs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParag%20hammered%20seven%20fours%20and%20six%20sixes%2C%20and%20took%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Anrich%20Nortje%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F64072-anrich-nortje-playerprofile%5C%22%3EAnrich%20Nortje%3C%2Fa%3E%2