Of%20Migrants%20In%20US%20Workforce%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20death%20of%20six%20Latino%20workers%20who%20were%20fixing%20potholes%20when%20a%20Baltimore%20bridge%20collapsed%20highlights%20the%20crucial%20role%20immigrants%20play%20in%20keeping%20America%20running%2C%20say%20advocates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20it%20stands%20in%20stark%20contrast%20to%20the%20rhetoric%20of%20populists%20like%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20who%20cast%20them%20as%20criminal%20invaders%20ruining%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMigrants%20come%20and%20do%20the%20jobs%20that%20Americans%20don't%20want%20to%20do%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Luis%20Vega%2C%20an%20activist%20and%20former%20construction%20worker.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20work%20is%20too%20hard%2C%20the%20hours%20are%20too%20long%2C%20or%20the%20conditions%20are%20too%20difficult.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWho%20here%20wants%20to%20clean%20hotel%20rooms%3F%20Who%20wants%20to%20work%20under%20the%20hot%20sun%3F%20Who%20wants%20to%20be%20in%20the%20fields%3F%26quot%3B%20said%20Vega.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20team%20of%20eight%20men%20was%20doing%20road%20maintenance%20overnight%20Monday%20into%20Tuesday%20on%20the%20Francis%20Scott%20Key%20Bridge%20when%20a%20huge%20container%20ship%20smashed%20into%20a%20support%20pillar%2C%20sending%20almost%20the%20entire%20span%20crashing%20into%20the%20Patapsco%20River.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20were%20pulled%20alive%20from%20the%20water%2C%20but%20six%20died%3B%20brothers%2C%20husbands%2C%20and%20fathers%20from%20Mexico%2C%20Guatemala%2C%20El%20Salvador%2C%20and%20Honduras.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BImmigrants%20--%20we%20get%20the%20job%20done%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20senior%20White%20House%20adviser%20Tom%20Perez%2C%20himself%20a%20Latino.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20six%20people%20who%20perished%2C%20the%20two%20others%20who%20survived...%20this%20is%20America%2C%20the%20immigrants%20(were)%20repairing%20potholes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20tragedy%20comes%20at%20a%20time%20many%20Latinos%20feel%20they%20are%20under%20assault%20from%20sections%20of%20the%20political%20class%2C%20as%20the%20United%20States%20ramps%20up%20for%20a%20bitter%20presidential%20election%20in%20November%20between%20Trump%20and%20incumbent%20Joe%20Biden.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump's%20stridently%20anti-immigrant%20campaign%20includes%20suggestions%20that%2C%20if%20elected%2C%20he%20will%20embark%20on%20a%20mass%20expulsion%20of%20people%20he%20blames%20for%20crime%20and%20drug%20addiction%20he%20says%20are%20wracking%20America.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20former%20president%20doesn't%20see%20how%20much%20damage%20he%20does%20with%20his%20poison%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Vega.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTerrorists%20don't%20sneak%20over%20the%20US-Mexico%20border%3B%20they%20fly%20in%20on%20a%20visa.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20people%20who%20pay%20traffickers%20to%20smuggle%20them%20across%20the%20hostile%20deserts%20of%20the%20US%20Southwest%20are%20the%20people%20who%20end%20up%20doing%20the%20dirty%20and%20difficult%20jobs%20that%20Americans%20depend%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%202020%2C%20when%20we%20had%20the%20Covid%20pandemic...%20no%20one%20wanted%20to%20work%20closely%20with%20another%20person%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Vega.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20who%20did%20the%20work%3F%20The%20cleaning%20in%20the%20hospitals%3F%20Harvesting%20the%20food%3F%20It%20was%20the%20immigrants%20who%20risked%20their%20lives.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHigh%20Risk%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThose%20risks%2C%20even%20if%20they%20are%20not%20always%20fatal%2C%20as%20they%20were%20for%20the%20Baltimore%20bridge%20workers%2C%20are%20all%20too%20real.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Arizona%20the%20legal%20minimum%20wage%20is%20%2414.35%20an%20hour%2C%20but%2C%20says%20Javier%20Galindo%2C%20a%20contractor%20in%20Tucson%2C%20immigrant%20workers%20will%20earn%20only%20%2480%20to%20%24100%20per%20day%2C%20sometimes%20for%2010%20or%2012%20hours%20of%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20know%20what%20time%20you%20come%20in%2C%20but%20not%20what%20time%20you%20will%20leave%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPoverty%20and%20desperation%20force%20migrants%20to%20accept%20these%20wages%2C%20and%20to%20work%20in%20conditions%20that%20can%20be%20fatal%2C%20such%20as%20high%20temperatures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20official%20numbers%2C%20Latino%20immigrants%20comprised%208.2%20percent%20of%20the%20United%20States%20workforce%20in%202020-2021%20but%20accounted%20for%2014%20percent%20of%20workplace%20deaths.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20total%20number%20of%20deaths%20has%20also%20risen%2C%20up%2042%20percent%20over%20the%20decade%20to%202021%2C%20with%20727%20Latinos%20dying%20on%20the%20job%20that%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERoot-and-branch%20reform%20of%20migration%20into%20the%20United%20States%2C%20including%20regularizing%20pathways%20to%20work%2C%20would%20help%20to%20reduce%20this%20toll%2C%20say%20activists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20it%20would%20also%20alleviate%20what%20many%20say%20is%20a%20desperate%20shortage%20of%20labor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20a%20lack%20of%20manpower%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Galindo%2C%20whose%20business%20was%20badly%20hit%20by%20border%20closures%20during%20the%20Covid%20pandemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2048-year-old%20began%20his%20working%20life%20at%20just%2014%20years%20old%2C%20clambering%20over%20rooftops.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou'll%20never%20see%20a%20white%20person%20doing%20that%20job%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20two%20decades%20since%20he%20started%20his%20company%2C%20only%20one%20white%20American%20ever%20knocked%20on%20his%20door%20asking%20for%20a%20job%20as%20a%20driver.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20didn't%20last%20long%2C%26quot%3B%20laughs%20Galindo.%20%26quot%3BHe%20walked%20off%20the%20job.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20region%2C%20he%20says%2C%20the%20construction%20sector%20depends%20almost%20entirely%20on%20immigrants%2C%20with%20the%20undocumented%20playing%20a%20key%20role.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20a%20feeling%20shared%20widely.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20we%20only%20hired%20people%20with%20the%20proper%20papers%2C%20things%20would%20go%20very%20badly%20for%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20Arizona%20contractor%20told%20AFP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20wouldn't%20be%20able%20to%20build%20what%20is%20being%20built%20in%20this%20city%20if%20it%20weren't%20for%20undocumented%20workers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711849620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fhr28lr4o_baltimore-bridge-collapse-afp_625x300_31_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fbaltimore-tragedy-highlights-role-of-migrants-in-us-workforce-5343185%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20death%20of%20six%20Latino%20workers%20who%20were%20fixing%20potholes%20when%20a%20Baltimore%20bridge%20collapsed%20highlights%20the%20crucial%20role%20immigrants%20play%20in%20keeping%20America%20running%2C%20say%20advocates.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fbaltimore-tragedy-highlights-role-of-migrants-in-us-workforce-5343185%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Marry%20Again%20Now%20If%20You%20Want%2C%20Or%20Face%20Jail%20After%20UCC%3A%20Himanta%20Sarma%20To%20MP%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWeeks%20ahead%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20Assam%20Chief%20Minister%20Himanta%20Biswa%20Sarma%20has%20taken%20a%20dig%20at%20AIUDF%20chief%20Badruddin%20Ajmal%20and%20said%20that%20if%20the%20Dhubri%20MP%20wants%20to%20marry%20again%2C%20he%20shou