0the%20UK%20to%20benefit%20from%20a%20pioneering%20CAR%20T%20therapy%20called%20tisagenlecleucel%20(Kymriah)%20thanks%20to%20its%20Cancer%20Drugs%20Fund%20(CDF).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20comes%20as%20the%20National%20Health%20Service%20(NHS)%20marks%20a%20milestone%20this%20weekend%20of%20100%2C000%20patients%20benefitting%20from%20early%20access%20to%20the%20latest%20and%20most%20innovative%20treatments%20with%20the%20help%20of%20CDF.%20The%20undisclosed%20cost%20of%20such%20treatments%20is%20covered%20by%20the%20fund.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20life%20has%20changed%20so%20much%20since%20I%20received%20the%20CAR%20T%20therapy%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Thakkar%2C%20who%20thanked%20Great%20Ormond%20Street%20Hospital%20(GOSH)%20in%20London%20for%20the%20%26quot%3Bincredible%26quot%3B%20care%20he%20received.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20remember%20I%20had%20to%20take%20so%20many%20trips%20to%20hospital%20and%20had%20long%20periods%20out%20of%20school...%20They%20have%20helped%20me%20recover%20to%20a%20state%20where%20I%20am%20able%20to%20enjoy%20so%20many%20things%20I%20love%20doing%2C%20such%20as%20playing%20snooker%20or%20pool%2C%20meeting%20friends%20and%20family%2C%20and%20going%20on%20wonderful%20holidays.%20It's%20hard%20to%20imagine%20how%20things%20would%20have%20been%20if%20the%20treatment%20wasn't%20available%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Thakkar%2C%20diagnosed%20with%20a%20form%20of%20leukaemia%20aged%20six%2C%20received%20a%20treatment%20which%20modifies%20a%20person's%20immune%20cells%20to%20recognise%20and%20attack%20cancer%20cells.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20treatment%20began%20in%202019%2C%20when%20he%20was%2011%20years%20old%20after%20he%20relapsed%20following%20other%20treatments%20such%20as%20chemotherapy%20and%20a%20bone%20marrow%20transplant.%20His%20mother%20Sapna%20said%20the%20family%20had%20received%20a%20%26quot%3Bsecond%20chance%26quot%3B%20at%20life%20since%20the%20success%20of%20the%20treatment.%20Without%20the%20fast-track%20access%20available%20through%20the%20CDF%2C%20the%2045-year-old%20said%20there%20may%20have%20been%20no%20other%20way%20for%20her%20son%20to%20receive%20the%20life-saving%20treatment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20felt%20like%20our%20prayers%20were%20finally%20answered.%20We%20still%20feel%20so%20grateful%20for%20this%20chance%20that's%20been%20given%20to%20us%20and%20not%20a%20single%20day%20passes%20by%20when%20we%20haven't%20felt%20thankful%20for%20all%20the%20doctors%20and%20nurses%20that%20have%20helped%20us%20through%20this%20long%20and%20difficult%20journey%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Sapna%20Thakkar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CDF%2C%20which%20opened%20in%20its%20current%20form%20in%20July%202016%2C%20is%20used%20by%20NHS%20England%20to%20provide%20fast-tracked%20access%20for%20patients%20to%20all%20new%20cancer%20treatments%20approved%20by%20the%20National%20Institute%20for%20Health%20and%20Care%20Excellence%20(NICE)%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20gathering%20further%20evidence%20of%20long-term%20effectiveness%20for%20promising%20drugs.%20It%20allows%20faster%20access%20to%20more%20than%20100%20drugs%20to%20help%20improve%2C%20extend%20or%20-%20in%20some%20cases%20-%20save%20their%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTreating%20100%2C000%20cancer%20patients%20in%20England%20with%20innovative%20treatments%20through%20the%20Cancer%20Drugs%20Fund%20is%20a%20fantastic%20milestone%20for%20the%20health%20service%20to%20reach%2C%20and%20testament%20to%20the%20hard%20work%20of%20oncologists%20and%20their%20teams%20across%20the%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Professor%20Sir%20Stephen%20Powis%2C%20NHS%20national%20medical%20director.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20vital%20fund%20is%20helping%20ensure%20patients%20get%20access%20to%20the%20most%20promising%20drugs%20far%20quicker%20than%20would%20otherwise%20be%20the%20case%2C%20helping%20people%20with%20cancer%20like%20Yuvan%20receive%20a%20life-changing%20intervention%20that%20sets%20a%20path%2