'%20attitude%20as%20a%20problem%20in%20Congress%20right%20now.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20wave%20of%20lawmakers%20on%20Capitol%20Hill%20calling%20it%20quits%20in%20recent%20months%20%E2%80%94%20many%20of%20them%20citing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmtg-threat-oust-mike-johnson-backfire-ukraine-aid-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eentrenched%20acrimony%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20has%20been%20difficult%20to%20ignore%20as%20Republicans%20barely%20hold%20on%20to%20a%20razor-thin%20House%20majority.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20gridlock%20and%20partisanship%20that%20has%20become%20commonplace%20among%20lawmakers%20has%20also%20taken%20a%20toll%20on%20senior%20congressional%20staffers.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENearly%20half%20of%20upper-level%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.congressfoundation.org%2Frevitalizing-congress%2Fstate-of-the-congress%2F2012%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaides%20are%20now%20eyeing%20the%20exits%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20according%20to%20an%20investigation%20conducted%20by%20the%20nonprofit%20Congressional%20Management%20Foundation%2C%20which%20seeks%20to%20strengthen%20trust%20in%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20says%20that%2048%25%20of%20senior%20staffers%20are%20considering%20leaving%20Capitol%20Hill%20due%20to%20%26quot%3Bheated%20rhetoric%20from%20the%20other%20party.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Congressional%20Management%20Foundation%20sent%20invitations%20via%20email%20to%20over%202%2C700%20senior%20staffers%20in%20the%20House%20and%20Senate%2C%20and%20138%20staffers%20chose%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20survey.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmong%20senior%20staffers%20surveyed%20who%20said%20they%20have%20%26quot%3Bsomewhat%20frequently%26quot%3B%20thought%20about%20their%20departures%20and%20believe%20their%20own%20party's%20rhetoric%20was%20the%20culprit%2C%2059%25%20were%20Republicans%20and%2016%25%20were%20Democrats.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20'my%20way%20or%20the%20highway'%20attitude%20that%20certain%20members%20of%20both%20parties%20have%20%E2%80%94%20and%20in%20certain%20cases%20combined%20with%20an%20apparent%20opinion%20that%20they%20alone%20are%20fighting%20for%20the%20'best'%20version%20of%20the%20United%20States%20of%20America%20%E2%80%94%20is%20not%20beneficial%20to%20our%20constitutional%20republic%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20Republican%20House%20legislative%20director%20told%20the%20Foundation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDictating%20is%20not%20governing%20and%20governing%20requires%20compromise%2C%20which%20seems%20to%20be%20more%20difficult%20to%20obtain%20with%20recent%20classes%20of%20Representatives%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20legislative%20director%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20report%2C%20Democrats%20had%20a%20much%20higher%20level%20of%20anxiety%20than%20Republicans%20regarding%20their%20safety%20and%20that%20of%20their%20congressional%20colleagues%20(73%25%20vs.%2047%25)%20%E2%80%94%20a%20byproduct%20of%20harsher%20political%20discourse%20and%20the%20January%206%20Capitol%20riot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Republicans%20have%20largely%20sought%20to%20move%20on%20from%20the%20events%20of%20January%206%2C%20Democrats%20have%20continued%20to%20needle%20the%20GOP%20over%20the%20issue%20and%20are%20using%20the%20defense%20of%20democracy%20as%20a%20key%20talking%20point%20in%20elections%20across%20the%20country%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20physical%20and%20psychological%20toll%20of%20this%20place%20cannot%20be%20understated%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20Democratic%20House%20staff%20director%20told%20the%20Foundation.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20in%20danger%20as%20a%20nation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20start%20of%20the%20118th%20Congress%20in%20January%202023%2C%20several%20lawmakers%20have%20left%20the%20House%2C%20including%20former%20Republican%20Speaker%20Kevin%20McCarthy%20of%20California%2C%20former%20GOP%20Reps.%20Ken%20Buck%20of%20Colorado%20and%20Bill%20Johnson%20of%20Ohio%2C%20and%20former%20Democratic%20Reps.%20David%2