st%20enough%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F6-missing-baltimore-bridge-collapse-presumed-dead-coast-guard-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epull%20two%20people%20from%20the%20water%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20were%20right%20on%20the%20scene%20immediately%20and%20making%20sure%20that%20they%20could%20be%20there%20to%20retrieve%20any%20survivors%2C%26quot%3B%20Dawicki%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BThey've%20just%20done%20an%20outstanding%20job.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPhilip%20Schifflin%2C%20the%20director%20of%20the%20Center%20for%20Mariner%20Advocacy%20at%20The%20Seaman's%20Church%20Institute%2C%20told%20BI%20the%20%26quot%3Brobust%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bthorough%26quot%3B%20search%20and%20rescue%20efforts%20he%20observed%20through%20news%20coverage%20made%20it%20likely%20that%20all%20those%20who%20could%20have%20been%20saved%20were.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20there%20was%20somebody%20on%20the%20surface%20of%20the%20water%20alive%2C%20they%20likely%20would've%20been%20found%20and%20recovered%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20mundane%20factor%3A%20timing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bridge%20was%20struck%20and%20collapsed%20early%20Tuesday%20morning%2C%20when%20there%20was%20little%20car%20traffic%20on%20the%20span.%20Video%20from%20the%20incident%20shows%20cars%20passing%20over%20the%20bridge%20seconds%20before%20the%20crash%2C%20and%20a%20local%20man%20crossed%20the%20bridge%20after%20an%20argument%20with%20his%20girlfriend%20moments%20earlier%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraph.co.uk%2Fus%2Fnews%2F2024%2F03%2F26%2Fson-got-over-baltimore-bridge-three-minutes-before-collapse%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EThe%20Telegraph%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHad%20the%20ship%20collided%20with%20the%20bridge%20during%20daylight%20hours%20or%2C%20worse%2C%20during%20rush%20hour%2C%20it's%20likely%20the%20number%20of%20casualties%20would%20have%20been%20far%20higher.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ETraining%20and%20technology%20can%20help%20limit%20disasters%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ECrews%20train%20for%20a%20loss%20of%20propulsion%20and%20steering%2C%20among%20other%20scenarios%2C%20Captain%20Michael%20Campbell%20with%20Massachusetts%20Maritime%20Academy%20told%20BI.%20He%20cautioned%20that%20it's%20too%20early%20to%20say%20what%20went%20wrong%20on%20the%20cargo%20vessel%2C%20called%20Dali.%20%26quot%3BI've%20talked%20to%20marine%20engineers%20and%20other%20captains%20and%20people%20were%20all%20speculating%20what%20went%20on.%20And%20you%20can't%20tell%20by%20the%20video%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Dali%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fship-caused-baltimore-bridge-collapse-previously-crashed-2016-antwerp-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecrashed%20at%20a%20port%20in%20Europe%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202016.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYet%20when%20a%20crisis%20does%20emerge%2C%20having%20drilled%20on%20how%20to%20respond%20can%20save%20lives%2C%20Campbell%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20big%20thing%20is%20with%20training%20%E2%80%94%20the%20more%20repetition%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0it%20becomes%20second%20nature.%20It's%20not%2C%20'OK%2C%20what%20do%20I%20do%20now%3F'%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECampbell%20said%20many%20operators%20in%20the%20maritime%20industry%20conduct%20quarterly%20run-throughs%20for%20situations%20such%20as%20a%20steering%20failure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShips%20heading%20for%20or%20leaving%20port%20must%20conduct%20systems%20tests%20within%2012%20hours%20of%20sailing.%20This%20includes%20checking%20propulsion%20and%20steering%20systems%20and%20other%20electronics%2C%20maritime%20experts%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDawicki%2C%20from%20the%20Northeast%20Maritime%20Institute%2C%20said%20students%20at%20the%20college%20undergo%20extensive%20training%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0from%20first%20aid%20to%20emergencies%20they%20might%20expect%20to%20face%20at%20sea.%20It's%20prescribed%20in%20part%20by%20an%20international%20treaty%20for%20professional%20mariners%20whether%20the%20ship%20is%20based%20in%20the%20US%20or%20elsewhere.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECampbell%20also%20said%20the%20technology%20on%20ships%20is%20much%20improved%20from%20when%20he%20started%20his%20career%20in%20the%201980s.%20There%20are%20safety%20systems%20%E2%80%94%20often%20brought%20about%20or%20beefed%20up%20due%20to%20earlier%20mishaps%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0and%20technology%20like%20GPS%20and%20widespread%20automation%20that%20have%20improved%20how%20ships%20operate%2C%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou're%20not%20relying%20on%20somebody%20going%20and%20turning%20a%20valve%20or%20something%2C%26quot%3B%20Campbell%20said.%20%26quot%3BThings%20are%20more%20controlled.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbaltimore-bridge-collapse-response-timing-mayday-call-saved-lives-2024-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711815887000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66070d8116bde8d4ead3c1d6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbaltimore-bridge-collapse-response-timing-mayday-call-saved-lives-2024-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20seemingly%20swift%20response%20from%20the%20US%20Coast%20Guard%20and%20the%20fact%20the%20collision%20occurred%20overnight%20could%20have%20played%20a%20role%20in%20limiting%20the%20tragedy.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22tparadis%40businessinsider.com%20(Tim%20Paradis%2CAna%20Altchek%2CGeoff%20Weiss)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A44%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbaltimore-bridge-collapse-response-timing-mayday-call-saved-lives-2024-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22BJP%20names%2011%20more%20LS%20candidates%3B%20fields%20ex-ambassador%20Sandhu%20from%20Amritsar%22%2C%22co