abroad%2C%20Varun%20Gupta%20and%20Ite%20Kaul%20longed%20to%20go%20back%20home.%20Born%20in%20the%20hills%20of%20Nainital%20and%20Kashmir%20respectively%2C%20the%20duo%20decided%20to%20start%20Himalaica%20near%20Nainital%20-%20a%20nature%20retreat%20inspired%20by%20chalets%20of%20Switzerland.'%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Tina%20Freese%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F345614%2Fnainital-homestay-himalaica-nature-retreat-stone-chalet-switzerland-kolar-river-vacation%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Want%20To%20Volunteer%20At%20Tourist%20Spots%3F%20Startup%20Connects%20Homestay%20Owners%20With%20Skilled%20Travellers%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20tallest%20statue%20in%20the%20world%2C%20the%20Statue%20of%20Unity%20has%20welcomed%20lakhs%20of%20visitors%20since%20its%20inauguration.%20Roughly%2025%20km%20away%20from%20this%20towering%20presence%20is%20the%20quaint%20town%20of%20Rajpipla.%20Located%20near%20the%20Narmada%20River%2C%20this%20once-princely%20state%20was%20the%20capital%20of%20the%20former%20Kingdom%20of%20Rajpipla.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHome%20to%20several%20royal%20palaces%2C%20waterfalls%2C%20and%20rich%20cultural%20heritage%2C%20it%20is%20one%20of%20the%20hidden%20gems%20of%20Gujarat%2C%E2%80%9D%20resident%20Ghanshyam%20Barot%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20tap%20into%20the%20rising%20tourism%20opportunities%20in%20the%20region%2C%20Ghanshyam%20opened%20%E2%80%98Rover%20Stay%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20a%20budget-friendly%20hostel%20with%20a%20rooftop%20kitchen%20in%20the%20royal%20town.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20unfortunately%2C%20most%20of%20the%20tourists%20would%20only%20visit%20the%20Statue%20of%20Unity%20and%20not%20come%20to%20Rajpipla%2C%20even%20though%20the%20town%20is%20roughly%2020%20minutes%20drive%20from%20the%20place%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%2038-year-old.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGhanshyam