ia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FMalathi-Sharma-Adukale-1710945587.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Malathi%20Sharma%2C%20co-founder%20of%20Adukale.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FMalathi-Sharma-Adukale-1710945587.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FMalathi-Sharma-Adukale-1710945587-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FMalathi-Sharma-Adukale-1710945587-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FMalathi-Sharma-Adukale-1710945587-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FMalathi-Sharma-Adukale-1710945587-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-345381%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EMalathi%20Sharma%2C%20co-founder%20of%20Adukale.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EUnderstanding%20Sankethi%20cuisine%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20dwelling%20further%20into%20Adukale%20%E2%80%94%20which%20has%20grown%20from%20a%2010%C3%9710%20square%20feet%20room%20to%20a%20business%20that%2C%20this%20financial%20year%2C%20is%20slated%20to%20generate%20revenues%20of%20about%20(USD)%20%242%20million%20(approx%20Rs%2016.6%20crore)%20%E2%80%94%20it%E2%80%99s%20imperative%20to%20gauge%20a%20better%20understanding%20of%20the%20Sankethi%20people%20and%20their%20cuisine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20January%202011%20article%20in%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20by%20C%20N%20Ramachandran%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Sanketi%20%5BSankethi%5D%20community%20is%20a%20small%20sub-sect%20of%20%3Cem%3ESmartha%20Brahmins%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20about%2025%2C000%20people%20who%20migrated%20from%20Southern%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20a%20few%20centuries%20ago.%20They%20are%20found%20mostly%20in%20old%20Mysuru%20state%20(espec