owing%20saffron%20in%20a%20100-square-foot%20room%20in%20Noida.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fsaffron-1711452013.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fsaffron-1711452013-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fsaffron-1711452013-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fsaffron-1711452013-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fsaffron-1711452013-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-345756%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EIn%202017%2C%20Ramesh%20started%20growing%20saffron%20in%20a%20100-square-foot%20room%20in%20Noida.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERamesh%20informs%20that%20apart%20from%20the%20one-time%20initial%20investment%2C%20one%20only%20needs%20to%20pay%20the%20electricity%20bills%2C%20which%20cost%20around%20Rs%204%2C500%20a%20month%2C%20and%20the%20labour%20costs%2C%20rounded%20up%20to%20Rs%208%2C000%20a%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSaffron%20has%20a%20good%20rate%20in%20the%20market.%20You%20can%20earn%20up%20to%20Rs%202.5%20lakh%20per%20kg%20in%20wholesale%20markets%20and%20Rs%203.5%20lakh%20per%20kg%20in%20retail%20markets.%20You%20can%20also%20earn%20up%20to%20Rs%206%20lakh%20per%20kg%20if%20you%20tap%20into%20the%20export%20business%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20reaping%20substantial%20profits%20from%20sales%2C%20Ramesh%20ventured%20into%20training%20others%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F341322%2Fhow-to-grow-kashmiri-saffron-at-home-vaibhav-aastha-maheshwari-patel-vadodara-gujarat%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eindoor%20saffron%20cultivation.%20%3C%2Fa%3EToday%2C%20he%20runs%20the%20%E2%80%9