20Increase%20their%20Incomes%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20a%20fisherwoman%2C%E2%80%9D%20Shweta%20Hule%20tells%20me%2C%20her%20voice%20crisp%20and%20urgent.%20My%20first%20guess%20is%20that%20I%20am%20delaying%20her%20from%20commencing%20her%20day%E2%80%99s%20work.%20But%2C%20as%20she%20explains%2C%20fishing%20is%20not%20on%20the%20agenda%20today.%20She%20is%20taking%20a%20group%20of%20tourists%20for%20a%20boating%20ride%20through%20the%20Mandavi%20Creek%20in%20Maharashtra%E2%80%99s%20Sindhudurg.%20This%20is%20a%20welcome%20change%20in%20routine.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBelonging%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F227428%2Finland-fish-earnings-how-to-farming-rural-economy-livelihood-microentrepreneurs-ngo-ang136%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efisher%20folk%20community%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20area%2C%20a%20majority%20of%20Hule%E2%80%99s%20day%20would%20be%20spent%20casting%20her%20net%20into%20the%20water.%20But%2C%20on%20the%20way%20back%2C%20she%20and%20the%20other%20fisher%20folk%20would%20allow%20themselves%20a%20short%20break%20during%20which%20they%20would%20sit%20back%20in%20their%20boats%20and%20revel%20in%20the%20beauty%20of%20the%20creek.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20evenings%20laden%20with%20baskets%20filled%20with%20the%20fresh%20catch%20of%20the%20day%2C%20the%20women%20would%20make%20their%20way%20back%20to%20the%20shore.%20It%20was%20during%20those%20moments%20of%20appreciating%20the%20beauty%20of%20the%20coast%20and%20its%20outlining%20mangroves%20that%20Hule%20began%20harbouring%20a%20dream.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20thought%20it%20would%20be%20lovely%20to%20bring%20tourists%20here%20for%20boating%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says%2C%20recalling%20her%20vision.%20However%2C%20financial%20constraints%20and%20a%20lack%20of%20aegis%20meant%20this%20remained%20a%20dream%20for%20many%20years%2C%20until%202016%2C%20when%20a%20ray%20of%20