ule%2C%20who%20had%20dreamt%20of%20something%20like%20this%20for%20years%2C%20was%20most%20elated%20when%20a%20UNDP%20representative%20made%20their%20way%20to%20the%20village%20in%202016.%20%E2%80%9CI%20told%20the%20representative%20about%20my%20dream%20and%20showed%20her%20the%20birds%2C%20the%20otters%2C%20and%20the%20trees%20near%20the%20creek.%20I%20told%20her%20that%20we%20could%20bring%20tourists%20here%20to%20see%20all%20of%20this%2C%E2%80%9D%20Hule%20notes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20official%20was%20more%20interested%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F260147%2Finitiative-saving-mumbai-mangorves-environment-godrej-and-boyce%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20mangroves%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20will%20you%20tell%20the%20tourists%20about%20these%20plants%3F%E2%80%9D%20she%20asked%20a%20perplexed%20but%20excited%20Hule.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20will%20learn%20everything%20about%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20Hule%20replied.%20She%20was%20excited%20at%20the%20prospect%20of%20knowing%20more%20about%20the%20vegetation%20that%20she%20had%20often%20admired%20herself.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20eager%20to%20know%20about%20their%20uses%2C%20benefits%2C%20how%20they%20helped%20the%20environment%20and%20more.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98Swamini%E2%80%99%20self-help%20group%20that%20comprises%20nine%20women%20and%20one%20man%20in%20the%20Sindhudurg%20district.%20The%20group%20earns%20around%20Rs%202%2C00%2C000%20a%20year%20by%20charging%20every%20tourist%20a%20fare%20of%20Rs%20200%20for%20the%20boating%20trip.%20They%20conduct%20a%20total%20of%20seven%20boating%20trips%20a%20day%20during%20season%20time.%20The%20women%20are%20supported%20by%20the%20staff%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F301797%2Fex-security-guard-prasenjit-mandal-helps-ba